{
  "stem": "2031.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were killed in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '39.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39, '40.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me and both brothers, my sister-in-law, and the children-- my brother got five children-- and my sister-in-law's brother-- we was 10 people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we was hiding from one place to the other, one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One time my brother says, we don't have any more other choice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know how they built the [INAUDIBLE] like a theater.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I helped them build.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a member there because he was living there, and the children went to the school, and the sister-in-law got the little store.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I know how the-- so we didn't get other choice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a Saturday, late in the afternoon, we went-- when it got a little bit dark, we went in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's a little-- big windows, but you can knock out a little window, and open-- there was like a screw to open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In this way, we opened one window, and we came in, all in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And within this [INAUDIBLE] was a door to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went into the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with two knives and one [? top ?] we made a little hole in the cellar, and we made like a drawer to go in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We made like a drawer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With the drawer we went in, and we made another drawer at the top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We put dark sand on it, as they shouldn't see us as a door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this way, we was laying there nine months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once a month, just once a month, when it was dark nights, my brother and brother-in-law went in to steal potatoes from the pigs where they was making-- also to bring water-- we should have something.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got one bag with 10 bottles, empty bottles.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
